Program: Great Lives
Title: Bernardo O'Higgins
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0076hlp
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Mar 2015
Writer Brian Keenan chooses Bernardo O'Higgins who liberated Chile in the 19th century. With Humphrey Carpenter. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? From 2003. Show less